cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GT, cs.MA, cs.CV 

The paper discusses deep multi-agent reinforcement learning in a partially observable, cooperative setting, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also proposes a benchmark problem for multi-agent learning, which falls under game theory (cs.GT) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). Additionally, the benchmark problem involves micromanagement challenges in a real-time strategy game, which could involve computer vision techniques (cs.CV).
